==French==

===Verb===
'''fournir''' 
# To [[supply]], to [[provide]]
#:''La boulangerie fournit mon restaurant en pain.''
#::''The bakery supplies my restaurant with bread.''
# To [[put in]]
#:''Fournir de l'effort.''
#::''Put in some effort.''
# (''cards'') To [[follow suit]]
# {{frslang}} To [[poke]], to [[shaft]], to [[hump]]; to [[have sex]]
#:''J'ai fourni ta mère.''
#::''I shafted your mother.''

